<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>TripTrakr</h1>
    <p class="lead">TripTrakr is a simple web app for users to add and organize their international travels by country, companions, and times, to aid in remembering them.</p>
    <p><a href="https://triptrakr.azurewebsites.net/Trip
" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Trips &raquo;</a></p>
